9-2707-4bdd-a26a-19523f1acb45\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>What is the \u201creference level\u201d in a spectrum analyser?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"d3ea2996-6ead-4c91-b69e-34e2d161e96d\\\"><p>True</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"f4c2c56f-c45e-4ea9-8c81-93785eb5f8d1\\\"><p>False</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"49c16e0d-8ebb-4879-a668-635cbc7107af\\\"><p></p></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi37b6bahyoubpnw4\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"0d2e9ab7-5d51-4d66-afe5-8fb1e666efc6\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>True or false?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>The \u201cpeak hold\u201d function captures and retains the highest amplitude values detected during sweep, which is useful for identifying intermittent or transient signals.</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"f329a97a-6573-4b96-bbec-c5d9bfbbdb65\\\"><p>By moving the antenna\u2019s azimuth rod furthest to the left and then to the right, while looking at the SA</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"85cd676e-e92f-446c-ab51-89a895f8f91c\\\"><p>By moving the antenna\u2019s elevation rod furthest up and then down, while looking at the SA</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36q4o4ufif114od\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"6fdea480-f06c-4f4f-9684-b2dcddbdaf45\\\"><p>By setting the start and stop frequencies (or centre frequency and span) to define the frequency range, allowing the SA to sweep through this range and display the signal\u2019s amplitude across the selected frequencies</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36sloo8pflxxtyb\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"ebed3a88-ade0-4f02-8f4a-34fc906cebbf\\\"><p>None of these</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36trgnpth8vrils\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"87c2d10b-aee2-4586-96e4-6cb9415bcd3b\\\"><p>All of these</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5klwi36q4o4ufif114od\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi37cxjfvv8ekzrza\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"98d55f0b-9eaa-4898-b413-51b06388aaaa\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>How do you perform a frequency sweep with a spectrum analyser?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"d3ea2996-6ead-4c91-b69e-34e2d161e96d\\\"><p>True</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"f4c2c56f-c45e-4ea9-8c81-93785eb5f8d1\\\"><p>False</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"49c16e0d-8ebb-4879-a668-635cbc7107af\\\"><p></p></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi37ddkfysl9hhlvi\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"278f725a-09a8-41ed-ad19-b9de82b075b5\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>True or false?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>The resolution bandwidth (RBW) is the bandwidth of the filter applied to the signal after it has been detected. It helps smoothing out the noise and fluctuations providing a cleaner display of the signal.</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"d3ea2996-6ead-4c91-b69e-34e2d161e96d\\\"><p>True</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"f4c2c56f-c45e-4ea9-8c81-93785eb5f8d1\\\"><p>False</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"49c16e0d-8ebb-4879-a668-635cbc7107af\\\"><p></p></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi37es7l4yywoqja5\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"b8f32d34-b1f5-4d55-8751-9a3007b4e8a2\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>True or false?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>The marker function is a tool allowing you to identify specific points on the spectrum display. It can show the frequency and amplitude of a signal at a specific point on the trace.</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"defc5581-d75d-486a-8c25-67f080d430b5\\\"><p>They are not different</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"69a0b759-4da3-4e15-b600-70a525f0cf3d\\\"><p>The only difference is that the spectrum analyser is the new generation, while the oscilloscope is the old generation</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36q4o4ufif114od\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"ec3a542b-ba23-49b3-b06d-57e1238371e4\\\"><p>While an oscilloscope displays signals in the frequency domain (amplitude vs. frequency), a spectrum analyser displays signals in the time domain (amplitude vs. time)</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36trgnpth8vrils\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"e20affe3-5506-4570-a2ae-009aaf805974\\\"><p>While an oscilloscope displays signals in the time domain (amplitude vs. time), a spectrum analyser displays signals in the frequency domain (amplitude vs. frequency)</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36sloo8pflxxtyb\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"ebed3a88-ade0-4f02-8f4a-34fc906cebbf\\\"><p>None of these</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5klwi36trgnpth8vrils\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi37fhhirm6nwg1pa\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"134673aa-0e50-43d5-b483-d2039b6c858f\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>What is the difference between a spectrum analyser and an oscilloscope?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"d3ea2996-6ead-4c91-b69e-34e2d161e96d\\\"><p>True</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi36pzprvm0hs11j6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"f4c2c56f-c45e-4ea9-8c81-93785eb5f8d1\\\"><p>False</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5klwi36rk82g9wvxmzsj\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"49c16e0d-8ebb-4879-a668-635cbc7107af\\\"><p></p></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5klwi37gv8ij3mzle4ha\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"5ee7232e-ed5c-41cb-877f-a0c2d1b849a5\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>True or false?</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><strong>Spectrum analysers are available in both analogue and digital forms.</strong></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 28, 57); text-decoration: inherit;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: inherit;\\\">Choose the correct option.</span></span></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"}],\"title\":\"Marlink, Spectrum analyser\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-06-22T17:13:42Z\",\"version\":1},{\"author_id\":\"auth0|671e98d0-b37b-0131-2ee8-22000b2f96a1\",\"deleted\":false,\"folder_id\":null,\"id\":\"sva312lyqstsqxtv1liq2oe9\",\"last_edited_by\":\"auth0|671e98d0-b37b-0131-2ee8-22000b2f96a1\",\"questions\":[{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37iaux310pc8pui\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"3329ba80-bc1b-4023-8508-2856377fbfaf\\\"><p>Betreff</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37jj3fxkingc0rj\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"fb2f9c59-3c55-41e6-b53f-8d832c16a43f\\\"><p>Absender</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37kzydwjil2y08j\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"cea3bda6-607f-4d81-8c13-bac06ddaa74e\\\"><p>Adressat</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37lkbbtkfnq68q2\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"fa99913e-c82f-40ae-9300-2a088198ff1e\\\"><p>Anhang</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37mampgd6iowz9f\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"98c66038-ba81-4cb6-a1d3-f70607c21421\\\"><p>Text</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37nzgq9fomhzzs6\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"dc80e714-324c-4b76-b966-01cc6745105a\\\"><p>Es gibt keine Gefahr</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5oizi37jj3fxkingc0rj\",\"corrects\":[],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"f3561c32-c8c5-4be2-9210-4a2db41636e3\\\"><p>Die E-Mail-Adresse von Frau Musterfrau enth\u00e4lt einen Buchstabenaustausch. Solche kleinen Ver\u00e4nderungen \u2013 wie ein \u201am\u2018, das durch \u201arn\u2018 ersetzt wird \u2013 sind typische Phishing-Taktiken.</p></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37hb0e0sff6l8ln\",\"media\":{\"image\":{\"align\":\"left\",\"alt\":\"Betreff: Informationen zu Ihrem letzten Meeting Absender: musterfrau@naheirnst.com An: info@wohnstadt.de  Hallo,  anbei finden Sie die vereinbarten Unterlagen aus unserem letzten Termin. Bitte pr\u00fcfen Sie diese m\u00f6glichst bis morgen fr\u00fch.  Mit freundlichen Gr\u00fc\u00dfen Lisa Musterfrau HR-Team Naheimst GmbH\",\"crushed_key\":\"rise/courses/QlbM3eNw5dfjmzEnovOHMCLRUGzAZhfc/OS_OUtxeJDEBYd0N.svg\",\"fill_width\":false,\"key\":\"rise/courses/QlbM3eNw5dfjmzEnovOHMCLRUGzAZhfc/MMKWUsvvdZ9foRut-III-05-2.svg\",\"original_url\":\"III-05-2.svg\",\"sourced_from\":\"USER\",\"tracking_context\":\"block:knowledge-check:MULTIPLE_CHOICE\",\"tracking_id\":\"8bCgNZj6nl-bPuUhBVmKOvbEQ9ClQBnB\",\"type\":\"image\",\"use_crushed_key\":true}},\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"221b99cf-41a6-4a3e-b8a7-cf3fd8f57775\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2.2rem\\\"><strong>Schauen Sie sich die E-Mail an und bestimmen Sie die Gefahr.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem\\\"><em>Bitte w\u00e4hlen Sie die eindeutig verd\u00e4chtigste Antwort aus. Es gibt eine richtige Antwort.</em></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem\\\"><em>Klicken Sie auf die Grafik, um sie zu vergr\u00f6\u00dfern.</em></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37pgr2p8tpdebdq\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"5f8b9ee7-bddb-405e-9b35-ed9477e1d394\\\"><p>Die E-Mail stammt von einer Adresse mit Ihrer Unternehmensdomain.</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"5179a602-e38f-4737-a2ba-83dd5dcd4822\\\"><p>Die Mail enth\u00e4lt eine dringende Handlungsaufforderung und droht mit Konsequenzen.</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37rrtdufpispt9l\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"970770f5-ebaf-4c57-bbbb-cebbf409d5e6\\\"><p>Die E-Mail enth\u00e4lt den vollst\u00e4ndigen Namen des/der Empf\u00e4nger:in.</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37s7zemghquu1x1\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"3a8fc0e7-5a75-447a-8140-b0b867450e2a\\\"><p>Die Mail wurde w\u00e4hrend der Abwesenheit des/der Empf\u00e4nger:in als automatische Antwort generiert.</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"corrects\":[\"cmqph5oizi37pgr2p8tpdebdq\"],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"c90a9add-4c11-432e-8574-0df42e4b3173\\\"><p>Phishing-Mails setzen h\u00e4ufig auf Druck oder Drohungen, um Empf\u00e4nger:innen zu schnellen Handlungen zu bewegen \u2013 z.\u202fB. durch Androhung einer Sperrung oder Fristsetzung.</p></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37ooohwg1nu19mz\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"261d62d3-fe13-4f97-b6e1-17db0e497b86\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2.2rem\\\"><strong>Was ist ein Hinweis auf eine potenzielle Phishing-Mail?</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem\\\"><em>Es gibt eine richtige Antwort.</em></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_CHOICE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37pgr2p8tpdebdq\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"76642757-4eeb-4b7b-9db9-74a5b3c02260\\\"><p>Ein bekannter Absender</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"0507c767-1785-4b58-8eed-0044c7be3f08\\\"><p>Unerwartete Links in der der Nachricht</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37rrtdufpispt9l\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"c6422111-57dc-469d-976c-9caf2e974a14\\\"><p>Aufforderung zu schnellen Reaktionen</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37s7zemghquu1x1\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"5f9bc022-73dd-4216-af2c-809a6a6f0158\\\"><p>Drohungen oder Belohnungen f\u00fcr sofortiges Handeln</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"corrects\":[\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"cmqph5oizi37rrtdufpispt9l\",\"cmqph5oizi37s7zemghquu1x1\"],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"2cc5f525-ec2f-4197-81c2-c9416c50fb2e\\\"></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37t3xpcldj7irxm\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"47d15cc7-13d0-46bc-b76a-6b96537eefec\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2.2rem\\\"><strong>Was sind Hinweise auf m\u00f6gliche Phishing E-Mails?</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem\\\"><em>Es gibt mehrere richtige Antworten.</em></span></p></div>\",\"type\":\"MULTIPLE_RESPONSE\"},{\"answers\":[{\"correct\":true,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37pgr2p8tpdebdq\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"76642757-4eeb-4b7b-9db9-74a5b3c02260\\\"><p>Ich \u00fcberpr\u00fcfe den Absender auf z. B. Zahlendreher, falsche Domains.</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":false,\"feedback\":\"\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"0507c767-1785-4b58-8eed-0044c7be3f08\\\"><p>Ich kann bedenkenlos auf einen in der E-Mail enthaltenen Link klicken.</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37rrtdufpispt9l\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"c6422111-57dc-469d-976c-9caf2e974a14\\\"><p>Ich antworte niemals auf Nachrichten unbekannter Herkunft.</p></div>\"},{\"correct\":true,\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37s7zemghquu1x1\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"5f9bc022-73dd-4216-af2c-809a6a6f0158\\\"><p>Ich nutze die \u201eNachricht melden\u201c Funktion in meinem E-Mail-Programm, um die verd\u00e4chtige Nachricht an die IT zu melden.</p></div>\"}],\"correct\":\"cmqph5oizi37qf74eyhp5r3gu\",\"corrects\":[\"cmqph5oizi37rrtdufpispt9l\",\"cmqph5oizi37s7zemghquu1x1\",\"cmqph5oizi37pgr2p8tpdebdq\"],\"feedback\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"2cc5f525-ec2f-4197-81c2-c9416c50fb2e\\\"></div>\",\"id\":\"cmqph5oizi37ute98uikon1li\",\"title\":\"<div data-editor-id=\\\"e3b15e03-24b7-4908-bafb-3e980e579b0d\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 2.2rem\\\"><strong>Wie reagiere ich richtig, wenn ich eine verd\u00e4chtige E-Mail erhalten habe?</strong></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1.7rem\\\"><em>Es gibt mehrere richtige Antworten